name: OCKAnyOutcomeQuery
desc: A protocol required for outcome queries, which provides customizing and sorting query results for outcome data.

items.name: init(OCKAnyOutcomeQuery)
items.desc: Creates a new outcome query from a specific query.

items.name: var taskIDs: [String]
items.desc: An array of task identifiers you can use to match outcomes in the query-returned results.

items.name: var sortDescriptors: [OCKOutcomeSortDescriptor]
items.desc: The order in which you want to sort the query results.
